data.description: Short Sale. Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house nestled in the heart of Deltona! This well-maintained property offers the perfect blend of comfort and style.    As you enter, you'll be greeted by an inviting living room that flows seamlessly into the dining area, creating a warm and welcoming space for family and friends. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and plenty of cabinet space, making meal preparation a breeze.    One of the highlights of this home is the delightful Florida room, where you can soak up the Florida sunshine year-round. It's an ideal spot for morning coffee or relaxation with a good book.    The primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom, providing a private retreat after a long day. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility for guests, a home office, or hobbies.    Step outside into your own piece of paradise - a fenced-in yard that's perfect for pets to roam or hosting outdoor gatherings. Whether it's a barbecue or a game of catch, this space is ready for your enjoyment.    Conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping, this home offers the ideal combination of suburban tranquility and urban convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely Deltona house your forever home!
